nodes.text: During the Galactic Civil War, eleven months after the Battle of Endor in 5 ABY, an attack led by Colonel Soran Keize of the 204th Imperial Fighter Wing was launched on the planet Dybbron III as part of Operation: Cinder. The attack resulted in the acquisition of a pirate gunship from the evidence yards on the planet, as well as the recruitment of Heirorius and Starzha into the fighter wing.
